== Short Bio
I am a research and teaching assistant associated with the [https://www.ist.uni-stuttgart.de Institute for Systems Theory and Automatic Control] at the [https://www.uni-stuttgart.de University of Stuttgart]. I received a B.Eng. degree in Mechanical Engineering from [https://www.th-deg.de/en Deggendorf Institute of Technology] and a M.Sc. degree in Engineering Cybernetics from the [https://www.uni-stuttgart.de/en University of Stuttgart].

== News
- *June 2021*. The paper "[https://epubs.siam.org/doi/abs/10.1137/20M1323679 Second-order dynamics with Hessian-driven damping for linearly constrained convex minimization]" was accepted for publication in SIAM Journal on Control and Optimization.

